divs: Sighting DetailsThe following report was taken by the dispatch operator. Witess was driving on the Staten Island Express between exits 11 and 12 when he noticed a very bright, silver, cigar shaped obect. It was not a plane or copter. He would like to know if anyone else saw this object. Lisa Behr-Dispatch Operator
